OL,4,CMPs call for 'complete reset' of music
OL,5,Cstreaming to ensure fair pay for
OL,6,Cartists
OL,7, The music industry is weighted against
OL,8, artists, with even successful pop stars
OL,9, seeing "pitiful returns" from
OL,10, streaming, a committee of MPs has said.
OL,12,FThey are calling for a "complete reset"
OL,13,Fof the market, with musicians given a
OL,14,F"fair share" of the #736.5 million that
OL,15,FUK record labels earn from streaming.
OL,17,FIn a report, they said royalties should
OL,18,Fbe split 50/50, instead of the current
OL,19,Frate, where artists receive about 16%.
